{"type":"message","id":"e216ba4f","parentId":"d4ccdedd","timestamp":"2026-04-30T21:14:17.581Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants to share all his credit card balances and interest rates so I can help him create a payoff game plan. Let me ask him to share those details.\n","thinkingSignature":"ab3d8c48f19c1d4ead0c712df6f9dae681dada3e4c880c8ee3be218d9bb74a37"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nLove it! Let's build you a solid payoff strategy.\n\nGo ahead and drop me:\n\n1. **Card name** (Capital One Platinum, Discover, etc.)\n2. **Current balance**\n3. **Interest rate (APR)**\n4. **Minimum payment** (if you know it)\n\nI'll plug it all in and we'll prioritize which ones to attack first — highest interest first, snowball method, or a mix. 🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":32033,"output":125,"cacheRead":128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32286,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777583652885,"responseId":"0642f92542fa1a80890827ae6d90a277"}}
