{"type":"message","id":"d306c2d1","parentId":"c02ebaeb","timestamp":"2026-04-30T21:25:39.355Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me summarize all the cards Bobby has given me so far:\n\n1. Chase - Balance: $2,300.90 | APR: 27.49% | Min: ~$78 | Due: 28th\n2. Discover - Balance: $1,440.22 | APR: 0% until June 18, then unknown | Min: ~$25 | Due: May 15\n3. Apple Card - Balance: $1,971.95 | APR: 25.49% | Min: $64 | Due: 30th/31st\n4. Capital One Quicksilver - Balance: $12,826.77 | APR: 28.24% | Min: $441 | Due: 27th\n5. Capital One Platinum - Balance: $284.37 | APR: 28.99% | Min: $25 | Due: 15th\n\nThat's 5 cards so far. Let me list them clearly for Bobby.\n","thinkingSignature":"9271ad32822db2dacfbf2b6db723d8cf636d7d2814953be692d29a5d785bd8bd"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nHere's what you've got:\n\n| Card | Balance | APR | Minimum | Due Date |\n|------|---------|-----|---------|----------|\n| Chase | $2,300.90 | 27.49% | ~$78 | 28th |\n| Discover | $1,440.22 | 0% → June 18 | ~$25 | May 15 |\n| Apple Card | $1,971.95 | 25.49% | $64 | 30th/31st |\n| Capital One Quicksilver | $12,826.77 | 28.24% | $441 | 27th |\n| Capital One Platinum | $284.37 | 28.99% | $25 | 15th |\n\n**Total debt: $18,824.21**\n\nAny more cards to add? 🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":33200,"output":382,"cacheRead":192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33774,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777584335216,"responseId":"0642fbcf014915f6fe65d020847ff81f"}}
