{"type":"message","id":"9f4d47d4","parentId":"22e6d7b6","timestamp":"2026-04-30T21:26:48.998Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants me to set up cron jobs to remind him about the things he needed to circle back on:\n\n1. Chase minimum payment - $78 (needs to verify)\n2. Discover minimum payment - $25 (needs to verify)\n\nLet me set up reminders for these. I should set them for a reasonable time to remind him. Since he might be available during the day, maybe set them for tomorrow or soon.\n\nI need to use the cron tool with the format specified in SOUL.md for reminders:\n```\nopenclaw cron add --name \"[reminder name]\" --at \"[ISO timestamp]\" --agent finn --model minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7 --message \"Use the message tool to send exactly this ONE message to Telegram chat 8212808444 and nothing else: '[Bobby's exact message]'. Do not add any commentary, just send it.\" --announce --channel telegram --to \"8212808444\"\n```\n\nBut wait - for cron jobs with agentTurn, I can just have the agent be reminded and handle it. Let me think about the best approach.\n\nActually looking at the SOUL.md reminder format, it's for sending a specific message to Telegram. But these are more like \"remind me to check something\" - not a one-time message to send. \n\nI think I should set up cron jobs that will trigger me to check in with Bobby about verifying those minimum payments. Let me set them for tomorrow or next day.\n\nFor Chase minimum - let me set a reminder in 2 days to check in about verifying the $78 minimum\nFor Discover minimum - set a reminder in 2 days too, or maybe same time\n\nActually, the way cron works with agentTurn, the agent gets a prompt and then acts. So I can set it to remind Bobby to check those minimum payments.\n\nLet me calculate timestamps. Current time is April 30, 2026 at 5:26 EDT. \n\nI'll set one reminder for May 1st morning around 9 AM ET and another for May 1st afternoon around 1 PM ET, both to prompt Bobby to verify the minimum payments on those two cards.\n","thinkingSignature":"8ed44104831130affbe6330bfab1b0a77f604fe6c0dd7acd1d218cf6dd82d60d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zyfkjhx6g092_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"Verify Chase Minimum Payment","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"Reminder for Bobby: Check and confirm the minimum payment amount for your Chase card. He said it was ~$78 but wanted to verify. Follow up with him about this.","timeoutSeconds":0},"schedule":{"at":"2026-05-01T09:00:00-05:00","kind":"at"},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"telegram","to":"8212808444"}}}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zyfkjhx6g092_2","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"Verify Discover Minimum Payment","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"Reminder for Bobby: Check and confirm the minimum payment amount for your Discover card. He said it was ~$25 but wanted to verify. Follow up with him about this.","timeoutSeconds":0},"schedule":{"at":"2026-05-01T09:30:00-05:00","kind":"at"},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"telegram","to":"8212808444"}}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":33473,"output":743,"cacheRead":128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34344,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777584394678,"responseId":"0642fc0b5b1275b73e4e917a13bea397"}}
